{"tid":1373361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"撤啦 仲留系度做乜 仲衝做乜？","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:08:12.000Z","uid":24778,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6510898d9357d61473d7d864b7867ba3e3b0f0c","tid":1373361,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZxw7Me.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZxw7Me.png&h=59722c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線勇武根本系度打緊超限戰<br />\n<br />\n如果不是勇武每每用生命值去硬接<br />\n又點會迫到呢D咁血腥赤裸既不公<br />\n又點喚醒咁多人？<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n各有各做<br />\n<br />\n勇武搏完<br />\n到和理非出場啦<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n前線勇士<br />\n你地一定要好好保重<br />\n和理非不想見到你地受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f00089056c827ef4d802a6201d0f5afa427a1d","tid":1373361,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:20:23.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"b581ebddd35571f338a194bdb20929df7dba44d7","tid":1373361,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"d3523a940f9cb2f1e6093cf95f6d7242bc2f9f3c","tid":1373361,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:20:44.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"6cc5b96878c81add91db6dd25daee8141edaab92","tid":1373361,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"daa7dbfbe267d6ff266e6f0d2db2847b04ab471a","tid":1373361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"重申多一次，唔明點解前線要留既請入，前線只會係以下三種情況下徹退。<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/drpmgT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/drpmgT</a>"},{"pid":"183f8fbc88a44dbfc9fed5a0e0591638bbc4e6cd","tid":1373361,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daa7dbfbe267d6ff266e6f0d2db2847b04ab471a","tid":1373361,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco